mil.nga.giat.geowave.ingest.local

Interface LocalFileIngestPlugin<O>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - The type of data to write to GeoWave
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataAdapterProvider<O>, IngestPluginBase<File,O>, LocalPluginBase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLocalIngestWithMapper, GeoLifeIngestPlugin, GeoToolsRasterDataStoreIngestPlugin, GeoToolsVectorDataStoreIngestPlugin, GpxIngestPlugin, TdriveIngestPlugin

    public interface LocalFileIngestPlugin<O>
extends LocalPluginBase, IngestPluginBase<File,O>
    This is the primary plugin for directly ingesting data to GeoWave from local files. It will write any GeoWaveData that is emitted for any supported file.
